title: Holiday Home Makeover with Rachel and Ryan
overview: With three young children in tow, Rachel and Ryan throw caution to the wind, set themselves a gruelling renovation schedule and embark on the challenge of transforming a tired, sprawling property on the stunning South Coast of New South Wales into their dream holiday home.This has been a lifelong ambition for the power couple, building a breathtaking coastal escape for their family and others to relax, unwind and enjoy a home away from home.
